Our signature tri-blend fabrics come together to create a lightweight t-shirt that feels great on the skin. The just-right classic fit with curved hem, ribbed collar, and center back seam lend to an ultra-flattering look you'll love. Plus, it's made from recycled polyester for that super-soft, worn-in feel. Pair it with a nice jacket and heels for a night out or your fave Hanes sweats and a scrunchie for weekend chores around the house. You can't go wrong with Hanes Originals. BE YOURSELF IN HANES ORIGINALS - A stylish collection of cool, modern essentials designed for comfort, made for every body. SUPER SOFT & COMFY FEEL - Our best cotton, polyester, and rayon come together to make this soft and comfy t-shirt for women. RELAXED & FLATTERING - This women's t-shirt features a just-right classic fit and has a curved hem for a flattering and feminine touch. MADE WITH RECYCLED MATERIALS - A portion of this women's t-shirt was made with recycled polyester. COLD WATER WASH - Hanes recommends machine washing women's tees in cold water to reduce energy consumption.

post_title: Hanes Originals Womens Cotton Plus Size T-Shirt
post_content: BASICS THAT ARE FAR FROM BASIC. You'll see and feel the difference in quality and fit the moment you put on this Hanes Originals women's plus-sized t-shirt. We call this style the tee with the Goldilocks fit, not too tight, not too loose. It's just an easy body-skimming silhouette that's always flattering, especially with its slightly longer, subtly curved back hem. You'll love the soft, U.S.-grown cotton of this crewneck tee, as well as its versatility for layering or soloing. Other style details that make this tee a customer favorite are the slightly lower, ribbed crewneck and the center back seam that enhances the shape. We think you just might want this classic cotton tee in every color. BE YOURSELF IN HANES ORIGINALS - A stylish collection of cool, modern essentials designed for comfort, made for every body. A JUST RIGHT FIT - A body-skimming shape that Goldilocks would love, not too tight, not too loose. SHAPED TO FLATTER - A slightly lower ribbed crewneck and a curved back hem add feminine touches.
